sentences: Lee Lu-da (Korean: 이루다; born March 6, 1997), better known by the mononym Luda, is a South Korean singer.
Luda was revealed to be a member of WJSN and its 'Natural Unit' on December 31, 2015.
In 2018, she was cast as a member of the MBC variety show Dunia: Into a New World.
Chocome, featuring members Luda, Dayoung, Soobin, and Yeoreum.
